Sometimes with #hepatitis C there are other #conditions that may appear. One of those is #cryoglobulinemia ..- April
#Cryoglobulinemia can lead to problems #ranging from #skin rashes and #kidney failure..-April
#Cryoglobulinemia is part of a #group of diseases that cause #inflammation and #damage to the #blood vessels throughout the #body..-April
There are #three types of #cryoglobulinemia and they are #based on the #type of #antibody that it produces..-April
The #three different types are : #cryoglobulinemia type I, #cryoglobulinemia type II and #cryoglobulinemia type III..- April

#Cryoglobulinemia Definition: Is most commonly associated with chronic #hepatitis C infection
#Cryoglobulinemia  It is also found with #endocarditis and other connective tissue disorder such as Sjogren syndrome.
#Cryoglobulinemia Presentation: joint pain, #glomerulonephritis, purpuric skin lesions, and neuropathy
#Cryoglobulinemia Diagnostic Tests: Lab tests show a positive rheumatoid factor and cold precipitable immune complexes
#Cryoglobulinemia Treatment: Treat underlying cause, especially #Hepatitis C with interferon and ribavarin
